description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Pyramid HIIT Row' from the channel Mike Dostal.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible. The The Firestarter vibe means Fast, explosive, and electrifying. Short but devastating. This is especially good for When you only have 10-20 minutes but want to give 1000%..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Test your limits with Mike during this high intensity drive. 

Max rhythm: 36, Format: Pyramid ...
